<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.7">
<l>āyiram kaṇṇuṭai yintira ṉārukkeṉ ṟāyar viḻave ṭuppa</l>
<l>pācaṉam nallaṉa paṇṭika ḷālpukap peyta vataṉai yellām</l>
<l>pōyirun taṅkoru pūta vaṭivukoṇ ṭuṉmaka ṉiṉṟu naṅkāy</l>
<l>māya ṉataṉaiyel lāmmuṟṟa vāri vaḷaittuṇ ṭiruntāṉ pōlum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lady, when the herders undertook a festival</l>
<l rend="indent">intending it for one-thousand eyed Indra,</l>
<l>It seems your son Māyaṉ, having gone there today taking the form of a spirit,</l>
<l>When all the goods that were served entered in by the cartload in vessels,</l>
<l>Having scooped it all up entirely and stolen it, has eaten it.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
